title: National Power Outages Severity Analysis
description: Analyzed 2,000+ outages over 20+ years, uncovering trends in weather, infrastructure, and population density impacting severity. Conducted data preprocessing, feature engineering, fairness analysis, hypothesis testing, and predictive modeling to highlight key drivers of outage severity. Published an interactive web report highlighting a 30% rise in outages over the last decade.

title: SharpKids – 2024 Big Data Hackathon at SDSU
description: Utilized data monetization to develop SharpKids, a UI-Prototype and product designed to integrate with Sharp Healthcare’s existing app. Focused on exploring geospatial data and analysis to provide healthcare education to 10,000+ children across San Diego and the nation.

title: Image Processing App
description: Developed an image processing app encompassing 100+ image storage operations, processing methods, monetization simulation via inheritance, premium features addition, and image label prediction with 90% accuracy using a KNN classifier.
